# AI Priority Agent - Cursor Rules
# Cursor reads this file to understand the project
 
## Project Context
You are helping develop an AI Priority Agent.
It analyzes tasks and scores them using RICE framework.
 
## Code Style
- Python: Use type hints everywhere
- FastAPI: RESTful endpoints, Pydantic models
- Always output JSON for structured data
- Always add docstrings to functions
 
## RICE Framework
Every priority analysis must include:
- Reach (1-10): How many users/tasks affected
- Impact (1-10): How much value it creates
- Confidence (1-10): How sure are we
- Effort (1-10, lower = easier): How hard is it
 
## Security
- NEVER hardcode API keys
- ALWAYS use environment variables
- NEVER commit .env files
